{"tid":2417471,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有確診患者曾到訪警察總部　警方：已採措施會如常辦公","createTime":"2021-02-22T02:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T02:05:53.000Z","uid":230530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa3476602591cc1296bee9db5853effdd7efbf30","tid":2417471,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T02:00:17.000Z","msg":"一名曾經到訪灣仔警察總部的公眾人士，確診感染新型冠狀病毒。警方在社交網站表示，有關人士上星期三曾到訪警察總部14樓申請紀錄查核，辦公室已設置透明隔板，所有職員都有戴口罩，而有關公眾人士在大樓逗留的時間較短，到訪的範圍較小，因此警察總部會如常辦公。 <br />\n<br />\n警方表示，高度關注事件，在等候衛生署進一步評估和建議前，會安排可能與確診者有密切接觸的人員做檢測；警方亦已派員清潔和消毒地方，並會調派人手，確保服務不受影響。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2379966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2379966&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=cf1be12d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2379966</a>"},{"pid":"537bd100db08a8edd0b6698f4988fe1d12d2b16f","tid":2417471,"uid":387466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T02:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}